high_descs: Take a step forward then turn left to face the microwave.
Take the apple out of the microwave then close the door.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the sink.
Put the apple in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the clean apple.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right and walk to the wall, turn right again to face the wooden table.
Put the clean apple on the table in front of the bottle of lotion.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean apple on a wooden table.

high_descs: Turn left and face the microwave on the counter.
Open the microwave door, take out the apple to the right of the egg, close the microwave door.
Walk to the sink to the right of the microwave.
Put the apple in the sink, rinse the apple with water, take the apple out of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the table on the right.
Place the apple down on the table to the right of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: To rinse an apple and put it on the table.

high_descs: Walk to the microwave on the counter to the left.
Open the microwave, pick up the red apple from inside and close the door.
Turn around, take a left at the table and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the apple in the middle of the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around, head towards the wall and turn right at the wall to face the wooden table.
Put the chilled apple in front of the blue bottle on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple on a table.
